comments:
Sometimes when eclipse is started my dynamic web project is not recognized as a 
dynamic web project but as an ordinary Java project (my guess). When this 
happens a lot of errors is reported for the JSP pages and such.

It can be fixed by restarting eclipse using eclipse -clean after which my 
project appears as an dynamic web project again. In order to get the errors to 
disappear I have to do a clean after having restarted eclipse.
